data.description:
Featuring this stunning open concept, 4 bed/3 bath home located in the highly sought-after Bridgeport community. This beautiful property offers an ideal layout with an open concept living, dining, and kitchen area on the main floor. There are also 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 baths, and laundry room on the first floor also. The large master suite boasts a walk in closet and glamour bath featuring a dual vanity, jetted tub, separate shower, and private potty room.

For added flexibility, the upstairs area is perfect for an in-law or teen suite, complete with a generous bedroom, closet, and full bathroom. Enjoy the serenity of the screened-in back porch that overlooks the expansive fenced-in backyard, which also includes a handy storage shed.

Convenience is key with this home's prime location near the Cape Fear Valley Hoke Campus and Ft. Liberty. Home is also centrally located to shopping, dining, schools and so much more. There is a $5000 allowance to be used at buyer’s discretion.
